title: Yeh Vaada Raha
subTitle: Vikram, in love with Sunita, faces tragedy when an accident leaves him unaware of her transformation, while Sunita, now under a new identity secretly hopes to rekindle their love.

title: Naach Uthe Sansaar
subTitle: A rich man's daughter falls in love with a farmer and wants to marry him. However, her father not only disapproves of this but also humiliates his mother, which makes the farmer seek vengeance.

title: Ek Nari Ek Brahmachari
subTitle: Raj lives with his brother, Mohan, who has taken a vow of celibacy. Trouble brews when Neena, along with her son, walks into their house and claims that Mohan is the father of her child.

title: Mome Ki Gudiya
subTitle: Ravi falls in love with Sheel but is shocked to learn that her marriage is fixed with his father. Even after his father steps back and Ravi gets married to Sheel, dark secrets loom over the newlyweds.

title: Neela Aakash
subTitle: Neela and Akash fall in love with each other after a comedy of errors. But her drunkard father disapproves of their union as she is the sole breadwinner of their family.

title: Jawani Diwani
subTitle: Vijay meets Neeta, the daughter of a Thakur, and falls in love with her. However, things change after he finds out that she has been promised to another man in marriage.

title: Aakhree Raasta
subTitle: A man is falsely accused of his wife's murder and imprisoned. When he sets out to seek revenge, he finds a police officer on his trail who turns out to be his own son.

title: Dost
subTitle: Maanav befriends Gopichand, a reformed thief, and helps him secure a job to turn his life around. However, Maanav suddenly disappears and returns just in time to support Gopichand during a crisis.

title: Nafrat Ki Aandhi
subTitle: Ravi Kapoor, a police officer and Sonu Dada, a former criminal join hands together to take down a notorious gangster, Chandi Das.

title: Ittefaq
subTitle: Dev Verma, a police officer, gets trapped in a web of lies when he interrogates two witnesses who also happen to be the prime suspects in a double homicide.

title: Awaara
subTitle: Born into poverty, Raj steals and works for a criminal gang in order to feed his mother. But when he meets and falls in love with his childhood friend, Rita, he vows to change his ways.

title: Awaara

title: Classic Legends
subTitle: Host Javed Akhtar presents the lives and careers of the greatest personalities of the golden era of Bollywood, as a tribute to their work.

title: Biwi O Biwi
subTitle: To overcome with his love for Asha, singer Chandermohan masquerades as an army officer when her father, a retired military officer, refuses to let her marry a civilian.

title: Do Jasoos
subTitle: Two bumbling detectives, Dharamchand and Karamchand, are assigned to locate a multi-millionaire's daughter, who goes missing after she witnesses a murder.

title: Shor
subTitle: Deepak, a young boy, loses his ability to speak due to a tragic accident. His heartbroken father, Shankar, works hard in order to treat him, but remains unaware of the fate awaiting him.

title: Toofan
subTitle: Separated at birth, the paths of Shyam, a lousy magician unwittingly roped into a crime, and Toofan, a defender of the people, cross again years later as they reunite to avenge their father.

title: Aadmi Aur Insaan
subTitle: Jai and Munish, fall for the same girl, ruining their bond with each other. However, an unfortunate turn of events reveals the true nature of their friendship.

title: Naseeb
subTitle: The lives of friends Namdev, Raghu, Damu and Jaggi take a turn for the worse when they win a lottery. Raghu and Damu murder Jaggi and frame Namdev who later returns to seek revenge.

title: Qayamat
subTitle: Two close friends turn enemies when one becomes a criminal and the other, an IPS officer. Wronged by his friend, the criminal swears to take revenge once he returns from prison.

title: Qayamat

title: Anari
subTitle: Rama, a simpleton, is appointed as the bodyguard of Rajnandini, a rich girl. She soon falls in love with him but her brothers' violent nature gets in the way of her uniting with Rama.

title: Videsh
subTitle: A drug lord escapes from India to Britain, assuming the identity of Swami Prem Babu to continue his illegal activities. When he learns that CBI Inspector Prasad Sinha is investigating him, he kidnaps Sinha's daughter.

title: My Life My Story
subTitle: The host invites prominent Bollywood celebrities who open up about their personal life and share interesting anecdotes based on their experiences.

title: Dulhan
subTitle: A girl is left distraught by the sudden death of her husband on their wedding night. However, things take a turn when a man resembling her husband arrives in the village.

title: Tamacha
subTitle: Raju and Vicky, two childhood friends, reunite after years apart. However, they end up on opposing sides of the law as Raju becomes a crusading officer, while Vicky descends into a life of crime.

title: Amardeep
subTitle: Raja, an arrogant man, is in love with his servant's daughter, Radha. He is enraged to find that she loves Kishan, so he hatches a devious plan to get them married and then keep them apart.

title: Itihaas
subTitle: Naina, who is betrothed to an influential man, falls in love and elopes with Karan, the son of an employee of her fiance. Soon, bounty hunters start hunting the duo to claim a hefty reward.

title: Coolie
subTitle: Seema, the daughter of a wealthy businessman, falls in love with a labourer. However, complications arise when Seema's father refuses to accept their relationship.

title: Pataal Bhairavi
subTitle: Ramu, a poor man, falls for a princess, but her father forbids the relation due to Ramu's poverty. Later, things take a turn for the worse when Ramu becomes rich, but it endangers his paramour.
